\mt1 Kalesia  
\imt1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rani m…ô n…ôfe i n…ôkuku…ô  
\ip Pol r…®m…ôrai n…ôkuku…ô i rev…ôn t…® nakalasia me ia profens riti s…ôv…ôi Rom kani m…ô Kalesia. Nakalasia me ia Kalesia n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha ram…ôvsaus…®ni p…®k t…® nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ô…°h…®nraha m…ô Juteiaisa me. Nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha h…ôni pen t…® n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel m…ô Kumwes…ôn tr…ôpw…ôh nuvehim…®ruien ir…ôha. Ir…ôha h…ôni m…ô n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel tuham…ôkeikei mhesi pen loa s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel r…ômwhen ia kuvehi ninhum m…®nraha, m…®ne n…ôniien nari, m…®ne nous…ôs…®mw…®nien ia n…ôp…®n s…ôv…ôi n…ôve…°…®nien asori me s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel. Nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha h…ôni mwi m…ô Pol r…®pkuvehi mh…ô nasoriien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô tuh…ôpw…ôh n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien in. Ia nukune n…ôkuku…ô i Pol r…®m…ôni pen t…® n…ôkur Kalesia m…ô n…ôfe n…ô…°kiariien amasan in ram…ôvisau. In rani mwi m…ô Kumwes…ôn ruvei pen nasoriien min. Ko k…®pkuvehim…®ru mh…ô k…®taha tr…®ni m…®nu…ô samesi pen Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses. M…ôt…ô tukuvehim…®ru k…®taha n…ôp…®n s…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Iesu Kristo. Nahat…ôt…ôien in n…ôha suatuk t…® nuvehiien n…®m…®ruien vi. Pol r…®ni m…ô tsahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu Kristo, mho nokeikeiien, n…ôn…ô mhar…ô ia N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Kal 1:11-12\x*Iou Pol. Iou aposol riti. N…ôrmama me h…ôpk…ôkwein mh…ô iou m…ô takowok i. I…ôrmama riti r…ôpw…ôh nuvehi ut…ôien iou, m…ôt…ô Iesu Kristo m…®ne s…ôv…ônhi Tata Kumwes…ôn s…ô r…®no r…ôtui mwi ia nemh…ôien s…ôv…ônhi, irau n…ôha krouvehi ut…ô iou.  
\v 2 Iou m…®ne pi…ôvmiaha me nepw…®n k…®maha m…®nraha ia kwopun i iahamrai n…ôkuku…ô i rauvehe tukumiaha nakalasia me fwe profens n…ôha Kalesia.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Rom 1:7, Fil 1:2\x*N…ôfwakiien s…ôiou m…ô Kumwes…ôn tata s…ôk…®taha m…®ne Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha trou…ôriari pehe namasanien m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien m k…®miaha.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Kal 2:20, 1Tim 2:6, Taet 2:14, 1Jon 5:19\x*Iesu r…®n…ôseni n…®m…®ruien s…ôv…ônhi memh…ô t…® noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®taha. In r…®no iam…®nha ir…ô m…ô truvehi raka k…®taha ia n…®t…ôt…ô …ôr…ôha i samar…ô ir…ô ipwet m…®ne. In remh…ô mesi pen n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn Tata s…ôk…®taha.  
\v 5 Pw…ôh n…ô…°n…ô…°…®niien rev…ôn tukwe ia nuk nuk me. Ou…ôh, pw…ôh ro iam…®nhi.   
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ô ro n…®p…ôrhienien kuatia a  
\p
\v 6 Iou iak…ôrk…ôrinari ia k…®miaha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôkwein k…®miaha m…ô tih…ôuvehe mhar…ô te…°…®n namasanien s…ôv…ôi Kristo, m…ôt…ô n…ôp…®n ouihi a rukurau, n…ôn…ô k…®miaha hi…ôuvei pen t…ôkutamiaha min, mamh…ôuv…ôn t…® n…ô…°kiariien amasan riti mwi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Wok Me 15:1,24\x*Iak…®ni iam…®nhi ir…ô m…ôt…ô n…ô…°kiariien amasan riti mwi riw…ôn. N…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ô ro n…®p…ôrhienien kuatia a. M…ôt…ô n…ôrmama nepw…®n n…ôha ik…®n kamho k…®miaha hiamhek…®r p…®k. Ir…ôha hokeikei m…ô tuh…ôuvsini n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kristo ruvehe n…ô…°kiariien …ôp…ô riti.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt 1Kor 16:22\x*M…ôt…ô iakani pehe tukumiaha i tr…®ni m…®nu…ô k…®maha riti u…ô a…°elo riti s…ô ruku pen ia neiai tr…ôvisau pehe m k…®miaha n…ô…°kiariien amasan riti rop…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien amasan n…ôha iah…ôn…ôvisau raka m k…®miaha i, pw…ôh i…ôrmama n…ôha rev…ôn ia napw.  
\v 9 K…®maha iah…ôuv…ôni raka n…ô…°kiariien i tukumiaha fwe kupw…ôn, n…ôn…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni tak…®ni mwi. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô i…ôrmama riti ram…ôvisau m k…®miaha n…ô…°kiariien amasan riti rop…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien amasan n…ôha hi…ôuv…ôuvehi raka, pw…ôh i…ôrmama n…ôha rev…ôn ia napw.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1Tes 2:4\x*K…®miaha hiam…ôf…ôt…ôr…®…° ir…ô? Ipwet m…®ne iakam…ômwur m…ô sin tr…ôkwein amasan ia nirak, i…ôrmama u…ô Kumwes…ôn? Rer…®miaha ramrhi m…ô iakam…ômwur t…® n…ôfe, m…ô tako n…ôrmama rer…®nraha ra…°ien tukw iou u…ô? Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô iakam…ômwur ihi m…ô tako n…ôrmama rer…®nraha ra…°ien tukw iou r…®pko mh…ô iou p…ôrhien i…ôrmama riti s…ô iakamo tukwini nari m Kristo.   
\s1 Pol ram…®ni irapw m…ô k…®n…ôfo ir…ô ruvehe mo aposol riti  
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Mat 16:17\x*Piak me, iakokeikei m…ô k…®miaha tih…ôukur…ôn n…ôri. N…ô…°kiariien amasan i iak…®n…ôvisau m k…®miaha r…®pko mh…ô n…ôvisauien s…ôv…ôi i…ôrmama.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Kal 1:1\x*Iapkuvehi mh…ô ruku pen t…® i…ôrmama riti. I…ôrmama riti r…®pkahat…ôn mh…ô iou ir…ô. M…ôt…ô iak…®m…ôuvehi ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha Iesu Kristo rier pehe tukw iou.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Wok Me 8:3\x*K…®miaha hi…ôuv…ôre…°i raka noien s…ôiou s…ô iak…®n…ôfo ir…ô kupw…ôn ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha iak…®nam…ôfwaki ihi ia n…ôfwakiien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel. Iak…®namomet…ô p…®k nakalasia me s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, mamousari m…ô takouraha ir…ôha.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Wok Me 22:3\x*Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha iak…®nauvehe mamskai ia n…ôfwakiien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel m…ôpi raka iou me nepw…®n t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iakamousari p…®k mamesi pen nar…ôien n…ôha kaha kupw…ôn me s…ôiou h…ôm…ôuvei pehe.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Aes 49:1, Jer 1:5, Rom 1:1\x*M…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn s…ô ruv…ôrfi raka iou fwe ia t…®pwi mama s…ôiou, in r…ôkwein iou, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô rer…®n ramasan tukw iou.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Wok Me 9:3-6, Kal 2:7\x*N…ôp…®n r…ôkwein iou ir…ô, rer…®n ra…°ien t…® n…ôseniien iou iak…ôt…ô T…®ni m…ô tak…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ônhi m n…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel. N…ôn…ô n…ôp…®n iak…ôtoni T…®ni, t…ôkwt…ôkwuni a iapkev…ôn mh…ô t…® i…ôrmama riti m…ô trahat…ôn iou.  
\v 17 Iapkev…ôn mh…ô fwe Jerusalem m…ô tak…ôtoni n…ôrmama me n…ôha ham…ôkupw…ôn ia nirak mho ir…ôha aposol me. M…ôt…ô iakier mev…ôn fwe t…ôn…ô n…ôha Arepia. Kurir…ô ir…ô iakr…ôr…®…° mwi mev…ôn fwe Tamaskes.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Jon 1:42, Wok Me 9:26\x*N…ôp…®n nuk kahar rukurau, n…ôn…ô iakut…ô pen fwe Jerusalem m…ô tak…ôtoni Pita. Iakuvehi n…ôfwakiien k…ôru fwe ik…®n k…®mrau min.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Mat 13:55\x*M…ôt…ô iapk…ôtoni mh…ô aposol me nepw…®n mwi, Jemes …ôpa, pi…ôvi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha.  
\v 20 (N…ô…°kiariien i iakamrai rauvehe tukumiaha ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn iak…ôpw…ôh neiku…ôien ir…ô.)  
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Wok Me 9:30\x*N…ôp…®n iakier ia Jerusalem, iakev…ôn fwe ia kwopun me ia profens mi n…ôha Siria m…®ne Silisia.  
\v 22 Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha, nakalasia me s…ôv…ôi Kristo ia t…ôn…ô Jutia h…ôpk…ôt…ô raka mh…ô iou, mh…ôreirei ihi iou.  
\v 23 Kamh…ôre…°i a n…ôrmama me kamh…ôvisau iam…®nhi m…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôm…ô i kupw…ôn ramomet…ô k…®taha, t…ôkwt…ôkwuni ram…ôvisau irapw nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®taha s…ô kupw…ôn ramousari m…ô trouraha.‚Äù  
\v 24 N…ôn…ô ir…ôha h…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni Kumwes…ôn tukwe iou.   
\c 2  
\s1 Pol rev…ôn m…ô…°kiari ir…ôha aposol me nepw…®n fwe Jerusalem  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Wok Me 15:2\x*N…ôp…®n nuk fotin rukurau, iakut…ô pen fwe Jerusalem k…®mrau Panapas. Iakiri mwi Taetas ruvehe k…®mrahar min.  
\v 2 Iakut…ô pen iam…®nhi t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®nahat…ôn raka iou iak…®n…ôtoni m…ô takam…ôkeikei mev…ôn. N…ôn…ô iakev…ôn m…ôtoni n…ôm…ô asori me s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me. N…ôp…®n k…®maha …ôpa, iak…®ni pen amasan t…® nir…ôha i n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôiou s…ô iakam…®ni irapw t…® n…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel. Iakamo iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iak…ôpw…ôh nokeikeiien m…ô narimnari me s…ôm…ôme iakamo m…®ne iak…®no raka, iakamo au…ôr a.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Wok Me 16:3\x*Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha Taetas k…®mrau min. N…®p…ôrhienien in i…ôm…ô Kris, m…ôt…ô ir…ôha h…ôpw…ôh n…®niien m…ô tukam…ôkeikei kuvehi ninhum min.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Kal 1:7, Kal 5:1,13\x*M…ôt…ô noien s…ôv…ôi nuvehiien ninhum m i…ôrmama k…®maha iah…ô…°kiari ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôrmama me nepw…®n kamh…ôkurir…ô afafa k…®taha, mamheiku…ô m…ô ir…ôha pi…ôvtaha me. Ir…ôha h…ôuvehe mamh…ôt…ô afafa k…®taha, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Iesu Kristo r…®neivinari ia k…®taha. N…ôn…ô hokeikei m…ô tuh…ôtoni m…ô sam…ôfar…ô ir…ô. Ir…ôha h…ônu…ô tuh…ôsis…ô…° mwi k…®taha ia natuak…ômien me s…ôv…ônraha.  
\v 5 M…ôt…ô k…®maha iah…ôpw…ôh n…ôseni ananien ir…ôha m…ô tuhasori ia k…®maha, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iahokeikei m…ô n…ô…°kiariien amasan i s…ô ro n…®p…ôrhienien trar…ô amasan tukumiaha mamev…ôn.   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Wok Me 10:34\x*Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha, n…ôrmama nepw…®n fwe ik…®n kani ir…ôha m…ô n…ôm…ô asori me. (M…ô ir…ôha hasori mh…ôfo pen ir…ô, m…ôt…ô iak…ôpw…ôh n…ôt…ôr…®…° penien ir…ô. Iou iakukur…ôn m…ô Kumwes…ôn ramo r…ômn…ômwhen a ia n…ôrmama me pam.) N…ôm…ô asori me n…ôha h…ôpw…ôh n…®niien n…ô…°kiariien riti mh…ôr…®p…®n pen ia n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ô iakam…ôvisau irapw i.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Wok Me 22:21\x*Ir…ôha h…ôpko mh…ô iam…®nhi ir…ô, m…ôt…ô h…ôt…ô sas m…ô Kumwes…ôn r…ômri pehe n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ônhi ia t…®pa…°e r…ô…°…®k m…ô tak…ôvisau irapw ir…ô ramev…ôn t…® n…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel. Noien n…ôha Kumwes…ôn ro miou r…ômwhen a mwi s…ô r…®no raka m Pita. Pita n…ôha ram…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn ramev…ôn t…® n…ôkur Isrel.  
\v 8 N…ôm…ô asori me n…ôha h…ôt…ô sas m…ô Kumwes…ôn ramasitu ia k…®mrau p…ôri ia wok mi n…ôha iarauo. Ramasitu ia Pita ia wok s…ôv…ônhi s…ô in ramo in aposol riti s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel, mamasitu mwi ia nirak ia wok s…ôiou s…ô iakamo iou aposol riti s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Jon 1:42\x*N…ôn…ô Jemes, m…®ne Pita, m…®ne Jon, i…ôm…ô mir…ôhar n…ôha kani ir…ôhar m…ô pos me s…ôv…ôi nimw…ôfwaki, n…ôp…®n ir…ôhar har…ôn…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn ramasitu ia nirak ia namasanien s…ôv…ônhi, haros…ô pehe r…ô…°…®nrahar mwatuk m k…®mrau Panapas r…ômwhen m…ô k…®maha kusen kuatia. N…ôn…ô k…®maha pam iah…ôseni m…ô tah…ôuai k…®maha me. K…®mrau Panapas tarouev…ôn rou…ôvisau m n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel, n…ôn…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôuv…ôn mh…ôvisau m n…ôkur Isrel.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Wok Me 11:29-30\x*M…ôt…ô n…ô…°kiariien kuatia a h…ôm…ôni pehe tukumrau i m…ô rer…®mrau tramrhi n…ôrmama me naut…ô s…ôv…ônraha riw…ôn, iarouasitu ia nir…ôha. M…ôt…ô n…ôri n…ôha iak…®n…ôt…ô raka takam…ôkeikei mo. Rer…®k ra…°ien tukwe.   
\s1 Pol r…ô…°kiari skai m Pita  
\p
\v 11 M…ôt…ô n…ôp…®n Pita ruvehe ia Antiok, iak…ôrer ia n…ônimen, m…ô…°kiari skai min, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ramo noien riti r…ôpw…ôh n…ômwhenien.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Wok Me 11:3\x*N…ôp…®n r…®m…ôuvehe vi a ia Antiok, ram…ôni p…ôri nari ir…ôha pi…ôvtaha me s…ôm…ôme r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel. M…ôt…ô kurir…ô ir…ô Jemes r…ôrhi n…ôrmama nepw…®n h…ôuvehe. N…ôp…®n hapirapw, Pita r…®nam…ôpw…ôh n…ôni p…ôriien nari ir…ôha n…ôrmama me r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel, n…ôn…ô m…®nam…ôrer …ôp…ô ia nir…ôha. In ro iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô rehek…®r n…ôkur Isrel me n…ôha s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôni m…ô n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôuv…ôn kuvehi ninhum m…®nraha t…® Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses.  
\v 13 N…ôn…ô pi…ôvtaha me nepw…®n s…ôm…ôme ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel h…ôhek…®r mwi, mh…ôkurir…ô ia Pita ia noien n…ôha ramo. Panapas mwi in rehek…®r, mukurir…ô ir…ôha.  
\v 14 M…ôt…ô n…ôp…®n iak…ôtoni m…ô ir…ôha h…ôpkesi pen mh…ô n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ô ro n…®p…ôrhienien, iak…ô…°kiari skai m Pita ia n…ômr…®nraha pam. Iak…®ni pen tukwe in m…ô, ‚ÄúPita. Ik i…ôm…ô Isrel, m…ôt…ô ik…®n…ôpw…ôh raka nar…ôien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel, mamar…ô ia nar…ôien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô r…ôfo t…ôkwt…ôkwuni ikam…ôrhi…ôrhi n…ôrmama me i r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel m…ô tuhar…ô ia nar…ôien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel?  
\v 15 Ia n…ôtuiien s…ôkrau kr…®nou…ôtui pehe i…ôm…ô Isrel mi. R…®pko mh…ô krau i…ôrmama mi s…ôv…ôi kw…ôn…ôkwus …ôp…ô riti s…ô n…ôkur Isrel kamh…ôni m…ô kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur …ôr…ôha me.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Wok Me 15:10-11, Rom 3:20-28, Rom 4:5, 11:6, Kal 3:11\x*M…ôt…ô krau krouukur…ôn m…ô i…ôrmama s…ô ramesi pen Loa s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel r…®pkatukwatukw mh…ô ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn, m…ôt…ô i…ôrmama s…ô ramahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu Kristo, in …ôpa n…ô ratukwatukw ia n…ônimen.\f + \fr 2:16 \ft Suatuk riti mwi t…® n…®niien n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha ia vas 16 in i m…ô ‚ÄúM…ôt…ô krau kroukur…ôn m…ô i…ôrmama r…®pkatukwatukw mh…ô ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn ia nesi penien Loa, m…ôt…ô nahat…ôt…ôien ia Iesu Kristo ramo in ratukwatukw ia n…ônimen.‚Äù\f* N…ôt…ôr…®…°ien n…ôha r…®no m…ô k…®taha mwi n…ôkur Isrel s…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Iesu Kristo. K…®taha samahat…ôt…ô ia Kristo t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô noien iam…®nha ir…ô tro k…®taha satukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn. M…ôt…ô s…ôpk…ôt…®…°ite mh…ô ia nesi penien Loa, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô i…ôrmama riti riw…ôn ko ruvehe matukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn n…ôp…®n ramesi pen Loa.  
\v 17 K…®taha i n…ôkur Isrel s…ôuv…ôuvehe raka t…® Iesu m…ô in tro k…®taha satukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn. M…ôt…ô m…ô k…®taha s…ôtoni m…ô k…®taha n…ôkur …ôr…ôha r…ômwhen ia n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel, r…ôfo ir…ô? Kristo ro k…®taha s…ôuvehe n…ôrmama kamho noien …ôr…ôha? Rek…ôm!  
\v 18 M…ôt…ô tr…®ni m…®nu…ô iakuvrh…ôk…®n mwi Loa n…ôha s…ô fwe kupw…ôn iak…®neitehi, noien n…ôha iakamo ramahat…ôn pen m…ô p…ôrhien iou i…ôrmama s…ô iakam…ôrui Loa.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Rom 7:6\x*Ia n…®karen s…ôv…ôi Loa, iakuvamh…ô raka. Loa n…ôha rousi …ôpune iou. N…ôn…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iakuvamh…ô raka ia n…®karen s…ôv…ôi Loa, iakukur…ôn n…®m…®ruien ia n…®karen s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn. R…ômwhen m…ô k…®n…ôrui t…ôrini pen iou ia nei kamarkuaui k…®mrau Kristo.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt Jon 13:1, Kal 1:4\x*R…®pko mh…ô iou iakam…®ru t…ôkwt…ôkwuni, m…ôt…ô Kristo ram…®ru ia nirak. N…®m…®ruien s…ô iakamar…ô ir…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni ia t…®pr…ôn…ô i, iakamar…ô ir…ô, mamahat…ôt…ô ia T…®ni Kumwes…ôn. In rokeikei iou memh…ô tukw iou.  
\v 21 Ko iapk…ôrarki mh…ô namasanien i s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn s…ô ruvei pehe miou. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô Loa in suatuk i…ôrmama tresi pen t…® nuveheien matukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn, ro iam…®nhi ir…ô Kristo remh…ô au…ôr a.‚Äù   
\c 3  
\s1 Sin ro n…®feifeiien ro n…ôkur Kalesia h…ôt…ô wau ia n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien?  
\p
\v 1 N…ôkur Kalesia, k…®miaha hiamarm…ôri! K…®n…ôvisau raka Iesu Kristo m k…®miaha r…ômwhen hi…ôn…ôtoni ia n…ômr…®miaha m…ô remh…ô ia nei kamarkuaui. M…ôt…ô n…®s…®m…ô n…ôha h…ôno n…®feifeiien mh…ôuvehi raka k…®miaha?  
\v 2 Iaku…ô tak…ôres n…ôresien riti tukumiaha i. Fwe kupw…ôn, n…ôp…®n hi…ôuvehe vi a mh…ôuvehi N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan, hiamo n…ôfe noien ro Kumwes…ôn ruvei pehe N…ôn…®mw…®n n…ôha m k…®miaha? Rosi hiamesi pen Loa s…ôv…ônhi u…ô? K…®miaha hi…ôukur…ôn m…ô r…®pko mh…ô iam…®nhi. M…ôt…ô k…®miaha hi…ôre…°i n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ônhi, mh…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô, ro pen Kumwes…ôn ruvei pehe N…ôn…®mw…®n s…ôv…ônhi m k…®miaha.  
\v 3 R…ôfo k…®miaha hiamarm…ôri iam…®nhi ir…ô? Fwe kupw…ôn, n…ôp…®n hi…ôuvehe vi a mhahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu, hiam…ôt…®…°ite ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan. M…ôt…ô r…ôfo n…ôha t…ôkwt…ôkwuni, ko hi…ôuvehe mhatukwatukw ia n…®skaiien atukw s…ôk…®miaha?  
