\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Dut 27:26\x*M…ôt…ô n…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôt…®…°ite ia nesi penien Loa m…ô tro ir…ôha hatukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn, Kumwes…ôn ram…ôkwein …ôr…ôha ia nir…ôha. Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ô…°kiariien i s…ô k…®m…ôrai pen ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan r…ôuiui ir…ôha. R…®ni m…ô, ‚ÄúKumwes…ôn tr…ôkwein …ôr…ôha ia n…ôrmama me pam h…ôpko mh…ô narimnari me pam k…®m…ôrai pen ia n…ôkuku…ô s…ôv…ôi Loa.‚Äù  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Rom 1:17, Kal 2:16\x*N…ôn…ô ruvehe m…®no nukur…ônien i t…® n…ôrmama m…ô i…ôrmama riti riw…ôn ko resi pen Loa n…ôn…ô muvehe matukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn. R…®no nukur…ônien i t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan rani m…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôrmama s…ô ratukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônhi, in truvehi n…®m…®ruien.‚Äù   
\m
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Rom 10:5\x*M…ôt…ô Loa in rop…ô ia nahat…ôt…ôien. Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Loa rani m…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôrmama s…ô ramo narimnari me pam n…ôha Loa rani truvehi n…®m…®ruien ir…ô.‚Äù  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Rom 8:3, 2Kor 5:21, Kal 4:5, Dut 21:23\x*M…ôt…ô Kristo ruv…ôfi raka nari ia k…®taha. Loa n…ôha ko r…®pk…ôkwein …ôr…ôha mh…ô mwi ia k…®taha, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Iesu r…®m…ôuvehi t…ômwk…®taha, muvehe mo in i…ôrmama s…ô Kumwes…ôn ram…ôkwein …ôr…ôha ir…ô. R…ômwhen ia n…ô…°kiariien i k…®m…ôrai pen ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan rani m…ô, ‚ÄúTr…®ni m…®nu…ô kousi …ôpune i…ôrmama riti n…®pwran r…ô…°her ia nei, ramahat…ôn pen m…ô Kumwes…ôn ram…ôkwein …ôr…ôha ir…ô.‚Äù  
\v 14 M…ôt…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Iesu Kristo remh…ô iam…®nhi, namasanien s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pen m Epraham ko ruvehe t…® n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel. T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®taha samahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu, s…ôukur…ôn nuvehiien N…ôn…®mw…®n n…ôha Kumwes…ôn ruv…ôni raka m…ô truvei pehe m k…®taha.   
