\v 15 Piak me, iaku…ô tak…®ni noien riti s…ôk…®taha n…ôrmama, mahat…ôn n…ôri n…ôha iakam…ô…°kiari ir…ô. N…ôp…®n i…ôrmama k…ôru krourai sun n…ô…°kiariien riti n…ôn…ô rou…ôrihi n…®pek…ô tukwe, r…ôknek…®n t…® i…ôrmama riti m…ô tr…®fi n…®pek…ô s…ôv…ônrau, m…ôrihi atukw a s…ôv…ônhi riti.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Wok Me 7:5\x*Fwe kupw…ôn, Kumwes…ôn r…®no promes me s…ôv…ônhi m Epraham m…®ne mwipw…®ni. Kumwes…ôn r…ôpw…ôh n…®niien m…ô ramo promes me s…ôv…ônhi m Epraham m…®ne ‚Äún…®mwipw…®ni me.‚Äù N…ô…°kiariien i m…ô ‚ÄúN…®mwipw…®ni me‚Äù ram…®ni n…ôrmama h…ôp…®k. M…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®ni m…ô ramo promes me s…ôv…ônhi m Epraham ‚Äúm…®ne mwipw…®ni.‚Äù N…ô…°kiariien i ‚Äúmwipw…®ni‚Äù ram…®ni i…ôrmama kuatia. Mwipwi Epraham n…ôha Kumwes…ôn r…ô…°kiari ir…ô in n…ô Kristo.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Eks 12:40\x*N…®pwrai n…ô…°kiariien s…ôiou ro iam…®nhi: Fwe kupw…ôn, Kumwes…ôn r…®no promes riti s…ôv…ônhi m Epraham, mar…ô m…®ni mwi m…ô n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha s…ôv…ônhi tram…ôkeikei muku…ô. N…ôp…®n nuk fo-hantret-toti rukurau, n…ôn…ô Loa ruvehe. M…ôt…ô Loa n…ôha ko r…®pkousi …ôr…ô…°r…ô…°i mh…ô promes n…ôha Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ômri raka m Epraham fwe kupw…ôn.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Rom 4:14, 11:6\x*Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô k…®taha sam…ôuvehi narimnari me s…ô Kumwes…ôn rauvei pehe t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô samesi pen Loa, noien n…ôha ramahat…ôn pen m…ô promes n…ôha s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn ruvehe muv…ôiw…ôn. N…ôn…ô ko s…ôpkuvehi mh…ô narimnari me n…ôha ruku pen t…® promes n…ôha. M…ôt…ô Epraham ruvehi narimnari me n…ôha Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pen min t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®no promes m…ô tro iam…®nhi.   
\s1 Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pehe Loa t…® n…ôfe?  
