\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Rom 5:20, Wok Me 7:38\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pehe Loa t…® n…ôfe? T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôrmama kamho noien …ôr…ôha me, ro pen in r…®r…®p…®n pen Loa ia promes s…ôv…ônhi, m…ô Loa tram…ômak meste mwipwi Epraham s…ô promes s…ôv…ônhi r…®n…ô…°kiari ir…ô truvehe. N…ôp…®n Loa ruvehe ir…ô, na…°elo me h…ôuvei pen m Moses, n…ôn…ô k…®maha iah…ôuvehi ia r…ô…°i Moses, i…ôm…ô s…ô ram…ôrer ia n…®mwrhenhi Kumwes…ôn m…®ne k…®maha.  
