\v 29 \x - \xo 3:29 \xt Rom 4:13\x*Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô s…ôv…ôi Kristo n…ô k…®miaha, n…®pwn…ôti Epraham me n…ô k…®miaha. K…®miaha n…ô n…ôkw…ôrhakw…ôrha me tih…ôuvehi narimnari amasan me n…ôha Kumwes…ôn r…®no raka promes m…ô truvei pen m Epraham.   
