\v 19 N…ôkw…ôrhakw…ôrha me s…ôiou. Iakre…°i iakam…ômis…ô p…®k mwi tukumiaha r…ômwhen ia pran t…ôkutan ram…ômis…ô m…ô tr…ôr…ôhi i…ôkunouihi. Takre…°i iam…®nhi meste k…®miaha tih…ôuvehi noien atukwatukw s…ôv…ôi Kristo ia n…®m…®ruien s…ôk…®miaha.  
\v 20 Ko ramo k…®taha m k…®miaha n…ôha t…ôkwt…ôkwuni, n…ôn…ô ko iapk…ô…°kiari skai mh…ô m k…®miaha. M…ôt…ô iou iakamar…ô isipw…®n, iakreirei m…ô tak…ôfo masitu ia k…®miaha.   
\s1 Pol rusipek…®n ia Heka m…®ne Sera  
