\v 21 K…®miaha s…ôm…ôme hiokeikei m…ô tihar…ô te…°…®n Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses, tiho mh…ôni pehe ro tukw iou i. Hi…ôuv…ôre…°i raka n…ôfe Loa n…ôha rani u…ô rek…ôm?  
\v 22 \x - \xo 4:22 \xt Jen 16:15, 21:2\x*K…®m…ôrai pen iam…®nhi m…ô Epraham t…®ni k…ôru i…ôrman. Pran s…ô in slef r…ôr…ôhi riti, n…ôn…ô pran s…ô r…®pko mh…ô in slef r…ôr…ôhi riti.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 4:23 \xt Rom 9:7-9\x*T…®ni slef r…ôtui r…ômwhen ia n…ôkw…ôrhakw…ôrha me nepw…®n a. M…ôt…ô t…®ni pr…ôn n…ôha r…®pko mh…ô in slef r…ôtui t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®no promes iam…®nha ir…ô ia pr…ôn n…ôha.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 4:24 \xt Rom 8:15, Kal 5:1\x*N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha ro n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô, m…ôt…ô ramasan m…ô iakusipek…®n ir…ô. Pr…ôn mi n…ôha k…ôru krou…ômwhen ia n…ô…°kiariien k…ôru Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôrihi t…ôrini …ôknek…®n. Pr…ôn n…ôha Heka r…ômwhen ia Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pen fwe t…ôku…ôr Sinae. Loa n…ôha ram…ôr…ôhi n…ôkw…ôrhakw…ôrha, m…ôt…ô ir…ôha slef me.  
\v 25 Heka r…ômwhen ia t…ôku…ôr Sinae fwe Arepia, m…ômwhen mwi ia taon n…ôha Jerusalem ipwet m…®ne, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô taon n…ôha ro slef ir…ô, n…ôn…ô n…ôkw…ôrhakw…ôrha me s…ôv…ônhi ir…ôha mwi slef me.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 4:26 \xt Hip 12:22, Rev 3:12, Rev 21:2,10\x*M…ôt…ô Jerusalem n…ôha fwe ia neiai r…ômwhen ia pr…ôn n…ôha r…®pko mh…ô in slef. N…ôn…ô in n…ô mama s…ôk…®taha.  
\v 27 R…ômwhen ia n…ô…°kiariien i k…®m…ôrai pen ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan rani m…ô, ‚ÄúA…°ien, pran s…ô ipk…ôkw…ôhakwen mh…ô! ∆èkwein …ôpw…ômw…®s, ma…°ien, pran s…ô ipk…ômis…ô raka mh…ô t…® n…ôr…ôhiien i…ôkunouihi! N…ôkw…ôrhakw…ôrha me s…ôv…ôi pr…ôn n…ôha k…®n…ôpw…ôh in, tuh…ôp…®k mh…ôpi raka n…ôkw…ôrhakw…ôrha me s…ôv…ôi pr…ôn s…ô s…ôv…ônhi fwe i…ôrman.‚Äù  
