\v 30 \x - \xo 4:30 \xt Jen 21:10, Jon 8:35\x*M…ôt…ô N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan ram…ôfni ir…ô? Rani m…ô, ‚Äú∆èrhi irapw pr…ôn n…ôha in slef irau t…®ni, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô t…®ni slef n…ôha ko r…®pk…®peki p…ôri mh…ô naut…ô s…ôv…ôi tata s…ôv…ônhi irau t…®ni pr…ôn n…ôha r…®pko mh…ô in slef.‚Äù  
\v 31 \x - \xo 4:31 \xt Kal 3:29\x*Ro pen, piak me, r…®pko mh…ô k…®taha n…®pwn…ôti pr…ôn n…ôha in slef, m…ôt…ô k…®taha n…®pwn…ôti pr…ôn n…ôha r…®pko mh…ô in slef.   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Jon 8:32,36, Kal 2:4, 5:13, Wok Me 15:10\x*Kristo r…®neivi raka nari ia k…®taha. In r…®no noien n…ôha m…ô nari riti tr…ôpw…ôh n…ôsis…ô…°ien mwi k…®taha. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô k…®miaha tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôrer …ôknek…®n, mh…ôpw…ôh n…ôseniien Loa n…ôha r…ôkwt…ômhiri k…®miaha hi…ôuvehe mwi mho slef ia k…®miaha.   
\p
\v 2 H…ôre…°i ro, iou Pol iakani pehe tukumiaha i, tr…®ni m…®nu…ô hi…ôseni kuvehi ninhum m k…®miaha t…® Loa n…ôha, nemh…ôien s…ôv…ôi Kristo tr…®pkasitu anan mh…ô ia k…®miaha.  
\v 3 Iaku…ô tak…®ni irapw mwi tukumiaha i. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô i…ôrman riti r…ôseni kuvehi ninhum min t…® Loa n…ôha, in tram…ôkeikei mesi pen pam n…ôfe Loa n…ôha rani.  
\v 4 Ik s…ô iku…ô tikesi pen Loa n…ôha m…ô tikuvehe matukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn, k…®n…ôrai raka ik. Ik…®n…ôpw…ôh noien kuatia k…®mirau Kristo, m…®n…ôpw…ôh namasanien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn.  
\v 5 M…ôt…ô k…®taha i sam…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®taha ia Kumwes…ôn m…ô in tro k…®taha satukwatukw ia n…ônimen t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô samahat…ôt…ô ia Kristo. N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan ramo k…®taha sam…ôskai m…ô tsameitenhi meste n…ôri n…ôha trier irapw.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt 1Kor 7:19, Kal 6:15\x*N…ôp…®n s…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®taha Iesu Kristo, n…ôri au…ôr a m…ô i…ôrmama riti kuvehi ninhum min u…ô k…®pkuvehi mh…ô ninhum min. M…ôt…ô n…ôri asori k…®taha tsam…ôkeikei mhahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu, n…ôn…ô mhokeikei Kumwes…ôn m…®ne n…ôrmama me.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 5:7 \xt Kal 1:6\x*Fwe kupw…ôn, k…®miaha hiamaiu amasan. Sin r…ôrer tukuaha…° k…®miaha m…®nise k…®miaha m…ô tih…ôpw…ôh nesi penien n…ô…°kiariien s…ô ro n…®p…ôrhienien?  
\v 8 Noien n…ôha r…®pkuku pen mh…ô t…® Kumwes…ôn s…ô ram…ôkwein k…®miaha.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt 1Kor 5:6\x*K…®miaha tiham…ôsiari. ‚ÄúYis ouihi tr…ôs…ô bred asori r…ôsisi.‚Äù  
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt Kal 1:7, 2Kor 11:15\x*M…ôt…ô iou iak…ôt…®…°ite ia I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha m…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha tr…®pkuvehe mh…ô mop…ô ia n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôiou. I…ôrmama n…ôha rameiku…ô ia k…®miaha, iou iakreirei m…ô in sin, m…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt 1Kor 1:23\x*Piak me, h…ôt…ôr…®…° ro, tr…®ni m…®nu…ô iakam…ôvisau ihi m…ô n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôuv…ôn kuvehi ninhum m…®nraha, r…ôfo n…ôkur Isrel kamhomet…ô ihi iou? Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô iakam…ôvisau ihi n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha, ko niemaha r…®pk…ôpi mh…ô ir…ôha. M…ôt…ô niemaha ram…ôpi ir…ôha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iakam…ôvisau irapw nemh…ôien s…ôv…ôi Iesu ia nei kamarkuaui.  
\v 12 N…ôrmama me n…ôha s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôni m…ô tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôuv…ôn kuvehi ninhum m k…®miaha t…® Loa, iakre…°i m…ô ko ir…ôha h…ôrai raka mwatuk s…ôv…ônraha, rer…®k ra…°ien!   
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 5:13 \xt 1Tes 2:16\x*Piak me, Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôkwein raka k…®miaha, m…®neivi raka nari ia k…®miaha. M…ôt…ô tih…ôpw…ôh n…®niien iam…®nhi ir…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúLoa n…ôha r…ôpw…ôh n…ôkwt…ômhiriien iou, ro pen iakukur…ôn noien narimnari me i noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…®pwrak rokeikei.‚Äù K…®miaha tih…ôpw…ôh n…®niien iam…®nhi ir…ô, m…ôt…ô tiham…ôkeikei mho tukwini nari m k…®miaha me, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô hiokeikei k…®miaha me.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Mat 5:43, Rom 13:9\x*N…ô…°kiariien riti n…ôha ia Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses r…ôuiui loa me pam. In i n…ô…°kiariien i rani m…ô, ‚ÄúTikam…ôkeikei mokeikei piam r…ômwhen ikokeikei atukw a ik.‚Äù  
\v 15 M…ôt…ô tr…®ni m…®nu…ô hiamahiahi k…®miaha me r…ômwhen ia kuri me, tiham…ôsiari kamo hiouraha pam k…®miaha me.   
\s1 N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan m…®ne noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…®pwrai i…ôrmama  
\p
\v 16 \x - \xo 5:16 \xt Rom 8:4, Kal 5:25\x*M…ôt…ô iakani pehe tukumiaha i m…ô tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôuvehi n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan mhar…ô ir…ô. N…ôp…®n hiamo iam…®nhi ir…ô tih…ôpko mh…ô narimnari me i noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…®pwramiaha rokeikei.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 5:17 \xt Rom 7:15-23, 1Tes 2:11\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…®pwrai i…ôrmama rokeikei narimnari me s…ôm…ôme N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan r…ôpw…ôh nokeikeiien. R…ômwhen a mwi N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan rokeikei narimnari me i noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…®pwrai i…ôrmama r…ôpw…ôh nokeikeiien. Noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…®pwrai i…ôrmama m…®ne N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan irau krou…ômw…ôki irau me. Ro pen r…ôknek…®n tukumiaha m…ô tiho narimnari me hiokeikei m…ô tiho.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 5:18 \xt Rom 6:14, 8:14\x*M…ôt…ô tr…®ni m…®nu…ô N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan ramiri k…®miaha, Loa n…ôha ko r…®pk…ôkwt…ômhiri mh…ô mwi k…®miaha.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt 1Kor 6:9-10\x*N…ôrmama me i noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…®pwranraha ramiri ir…ôha r…®m…ôru a t…® n…ôtoniien. Ir…ôha n…ôrman m…®ne n…®pran kamh…ôiri …ôpnapen ir…ôha me. Ir…ôha kamho noien me nepw…®n h…ômkem…®k m…®ne n…ôfe nari n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ônraha rokeikei.  
\v 20 Ir…ôha kamh…ôfwaki m n…ôn…®mwi nari me, mamho nahak, mamh…ômw…ôki ir…ôha me, mamh…ôvis…ô. Rer…®nraha ramrhi …ôr…ôha ir…ôha me. Niemaha ram…ôpi ir…ôha. Ir…ôha kamh…ôfi…ôut…ô ia nir…ôha me, mamho n…ôrmama h…ômw…ôki ir…ôha me mh…ôrai nar…ôien s…ôv…ônraha.  
\v 21 Rer…®nraha ramakres. Ir…ôha kamh…ôn…®mwi n…ôn…®mwiien skai mamhakon…ô ir…ô, mamho lafet …ôr…ôha me, mamho mwi narimnari me nepw…®n iam…®nhi. Iou tak…®ni pehe tukumiaha i n…ô…°kiariien i iakuv…ôni raka fwe kupw…ôn. N…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamho noien iam…®nha ir…ô tuh…ôpw…ôh nuvnimw…ôien ia n…®t…ôt…ô s…ô Kumwes…ôn ram…ôr…®m…ônu ir…ô.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 5:22 \xt Efes 5:9\x*M…ôt…ô n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan ramiri ir…ôha h…ôuku…ô kw…ônkwanraha s…ô ramasan me i. Ir…ôha hokeikei n…ôrmama. Rer…®nraha ra…°ien. Ir…ôha kamhar…ô ia n…ôm…ôrinuien, mamho n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha r…ôpw…ômw…®s. Rer…®nraha ramasan t…® n…ôrmama. Ir…ôha kamho noien amasan. Ia n…ôp…®n me ir…ôha kamh…ôkwt…ômhiri …ôknek…®n n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônraha m…®ne n…ôfe h…ôni m…ô tuho.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 5:23 \xt 1Tim 1:9\x*Noien s…ôv…ônraha ramasan m…ôpou. Ir…ôha kamh…ôkoui atukw a ir…ôha m…ô tuh…ôpko mh…ô noien …ôr…ôha. Loa riti riw…ôn ram…ôsis…ô…° k…®miaha m…ô tih…ôpw…ôh noien iam…®nha ir…ô.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 5:24 \xt Rom 6:6, Kol 3:5, 1Tes 2:11\x*N…ôrmama me s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo r…ômwhen m…ô h…ôn…ôrui t…ôrini pen raka noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…®pwranraha m…®ne narimnari me n…ôha noien …ôr…ôha n…ôha rokeikei p…®k ia nei kamarkuaui.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 5:25 \xt Rom 8:4\x*N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan rauvei pehe n…®m…®ruien vi m k…®taha. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô pw…ôh s…ôkurir…ô N…ôn…®mw…®n n…ôha.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 5:26 \xt Fil 2:3\x*R…ôr…ôha m…ô sam…ôfi…ôut…ô ia k…®taha me, u…ô samo niemaha m k…®taha me, u…ô rer…®taha ramakres narimnari me s…ôk…®taha me.   
\c 6  
\s1 K…®miaha tihasitu ia k…®miaha me  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 6:1 \xt Mat 18:15, Jem 5:19\x*Piak me, tr…®ni m…®nu…ô k…®miaha riti r…®mwei ia n…ôr…ôhaien, k…®miaha s…ôm…ôme hi…ôuv…ôskai ia N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôiri m…ôru in, pw…ôh r…®r…ôr…®…° mwi t…® suatuk amasan. M…ôt…ô tiham…ôsiari kamo k…®miaha mwi tih…ôre…°i noien …ôr…ôha ruvi n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha mo k…®miaha hi…ômwei.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Rom 15:1\x*Tihasitu ia k…®miaha me mh…ôvrani nari p…ômp…ôm me s…ôk…®miaha me. Noien n…ôha tiho n…ôn…ô mhesi pen n…ôkwai Kristo.  
\v 3 R…ôr…ôha m…ô i…ôrmama au…ôr a riti rer…®n tramrhi atukw a in, mam…®ni iam…®nhi ir…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúEh, iou i…ôrmama riti.‚Äù I…ôrmama s…ô ramo noien n…ôha rameiku…ô atukw a ir…ô.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 6:4 \xt 1Kor 11:28\x*I…ôrmama riti tram…ôkeikei m…ôt…ô sas …ôpa ia wok s…ôv…ônhi m…ô r…ômwhen. M…ô wok s…ôv…ônhi ramasan, rukur…ôn n…ôfi…ôut…ô atukwien in t…® s…ôv…ônhi …ôpa wok. M…ôt…ô r…ôr…ôha ram…ôfi…ôut…ô atukw a in t…® wok s…ôv…ôi i…ôrm…ôp…ô.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt Rom 14:12\x*Iak…®ni iam…®nhi t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôrmama kuatia kuatia tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôtui amasan t…® s…ôv…ônraha wok.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 6:6 \xt 1Kor 9:11,14\x*I…ôrmama s…ô kamahat…ôn in ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, n…ôp…®n ruvehi nari amasan riti, ramasan m…ô ruvehi pen n…®p…ôr…®n m iahat…ôn s…ôv…ônhi.   
\s1 N…ôfe nuni nari i…ôrmama tr…ôpwei tresi …ôpa mwi nukwan  
\p
\v 7 K…®miaha tih…ôpw…ôh neiku…ô atukwien ia k…®miaha. Hi…ôukur…ôn m…ô ko hiar…®s ia Kumwes…ôn? Rek…ôm! N…ôfe nuni nari i…ôrmama tr…ôpwei tresi …ôpa mwi nukwan.  
\v 8 Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô i…ôrmama r…ôpwei noien …ôr…ôha s…ô n…®pwran rokeikei, noien n…ôha s…ôv…ônhi truvei pen nukwan min, in n…ô i…ôrmama n…ôha tremh…ô. M…ôt…ô tr…®ni m…®nu…ô i…ôrmama r…ôpwei noien amasan s…ô N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan rokeikei, N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan truvei pen nukwan min, in n…ô n…®m…®ruien rer…®n.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 6:9 \xt 1Tes 3:13\x*K…®taha tsam…ôkeikei mho noien amasan, mh…ôpw…ôh n…ôpouien ir…ô, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô tsesi nukwai noien n…ôha samo ia n…ôp…®n atukwatukw s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 10 Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô, r…®no n…ôp…®n s…ôv…ônhi pw…ôh so noien amasan, mhasitu ia n…ôrmama me pam. Ir…ônh…ô ir…ô, tsam…ôkeikei mho iam…®nhi ir…ô ia n…ôrmama me n…ôha ir…ôha pi…ôvtaha me m…®ne k…®tirim…ôtaha me t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ir…ôha mwi kamhahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu.   
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien sampam  
\p
\v 11 H…ôtoni ro nukwai n…ôkuku…ô me i h…ôpwinari. Iakrai atukw ia r…ô…°…®k ia n…ôkuku…ô s…ôk…®miaha.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 6:12 \xt Kal 5:11, Fil 3:18\x*N…ôrmama me n…ôha s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôrhi…ôrhi k…®miaha m…ô tih…ôuv…ôn kuvehi ninhum m k…®miaha t…® Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses, ir…ôha kamho noien n…ôha m…ô n…ôkur Isrel tuh…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni ir…ôha. Ir…ôha h…ôpw…ôh nokeikeiien m…ô n…ôkur Isrel tuhomet…ô ir…ôha, ro pen h…ôpw…ôh n…ôvisauien nemh…ôien s…ôv…ôi Kristo ia nei kamarkuaui.  
\v 13 N…ôrmama me n…ôha s…ôm…ôme kuv…ôuvehi raka ninhum m…®nraha t…® Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses, ir…ôha mwi h…ôpw…ôh nesi penien Loa n…ôha. M…ôt…ô hokeikei m…ô tuh…ôuvehi ninhum m k…®miaha, n…ôn…ô kurir…ô ir…ô tuh…ôfi…ôut…ô ia nir…ôha ia n…ômri n…ôkur Isrel t…® noien n…ôha k…®no ia n…®pwramiaha.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 6:14 \xt 1Kor 1:31, 2:2\x*M…ôt…ô iou tak…ôpw…ôh n…ôfi…ôut…ôien ia nirak. Tak…ôfi…ôut…ô a ia nei kamarkuaui s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo, I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha. Ia nei kamarkuaui n…ôha iakuvamh…ô raka m…®n…ôpw…ôh raka noien me s…ôv…ôi t…®pr…ôn…ô i.  
